Commercial terms:
- Search is free. No fees for flight search, regardless of volume. Just use it.
- Booking fee: 1% of booking value (minimum $1 USD per booking).
- Payment is processed through Stripe Connect (other methods available on request).

In short: if you only need search, go ahead and use it — no agreement needed.
If you want to integrate booking into your product, contact us to set up a
commercial license between LetsFG and you (or your organization). It's quick
and painless — we typically respond within 1 hour.

Contact:
- Email: contact@letsfg.co
- Founder: adam@letsfg.co
- GitHub: https://github.com/LetsFG/LetsFG/issues


3. HOW THE SOFTWARE WORKS

The connectors interact with airline websites through your AI agent, on your
behalf, when you choose to run them. Each connector automates the process of
searching a specific airline's public-facing website or API — the same way a
human would search for flights in a browser. The Software does not access any
private, restricted, or authenticated airline systems beyond what is publicly
available to any user.
